@startuml
!include _yunlink_protocol_theme.iuml
title 协议分面与参与方
top to bottom direction

actor "Ground Station\nagent_type = kGroundStation" as gs
actor "Onboard Computer\nUAV / UGV protocol endpoint" as onboard
actor "Swarm Endpoint\nGroup coordinator or relay" as swarm

package "Yunlink Protocol" <<Neutral>> {
  component "Transport\nTCP / UDP" as transport <<Neutral>>
  component "SecureEnvelope Wire Layer" as wire <<Neutral>>
  component "Control Plane\nSession / Authority /\nCommand / CommandResult" as control <<Control>>
  component "State Plane\nStateSnapshot / StateEvent" as state <<StatePlane>>
  component "Bulk Discovery Plane\nBulkChannelDescriptor" as bulk <<Bulk>>
  component "SDK Layer\nRuntime / SessionClient /\nCommandPublisher / Subscribers" as sdk <<Neutral>>
}

gs --> sdk : typed API / protocol access
sdk --> wire : semantic message -> envelope
wire --> transport : route over TCP / UDP

wire --> control : control families
wire --> state : snapshot / event families
wire --> bulk : discovery / authorization

control --> onboard : single-vehicle control
control --> swarm : group target / broadcast

onboard --> state : periodic snapshots\nand sparse events
swarm --> state : group result\nand member feedback

bulk --> onboard : URI / channel metadata
bulk --> swarm : group bulk descriptors

note bottom of wire
统一信封总线只负责稳定承载：
transport 不定义业务语义，
message_family + message_type + schema_version 才定义语义。
end note
@enduml
